=== Solved problems ===
==== Syntax colouring colours? ====
[new] How is one supposed to customize the colours of syntax colouring? Yes, I know "M-x customize-group RET mumamo RET". But which fecking value? customize-face doesn't seem appropriate, since the current face is mumamo-somehting-background.

[new]
Syntax colours are part of Emacs, not nXhtml. If you want to customize them do

  M-x customize-group RET font-lock-faces RET


